## 9. Introducing GET and POST 

### GET â€” asking for data

Used to:

* fetch webpages
* read data


curl https://api.example.com/users
```

Meaning:

> â€œServer, please give me this information.â€

---

### POST â€” sending data

Used to:

* submit forms
* create data
* send login info

Conceptually:

> â€œServer, here is some data for you.â€


